2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper uses image analysis techniques to extract terms from photos and generate a story based on those terms. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper involves the use of machine learning models (LSTM and transformer) to generate stories. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper involves the use of machine learning models to generate stories. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves the retrieval of relevant terms from images to generate a story.
